# Careers content collection
#
# This directory is intentionally empty at launch. The /careers page shows an
# evergreen "we're always looking for talent" CTA when no role files exist.
#
# To list an open role, add a Markdown file here, e.g. `robotics-engineer.md`:
#
#   ---
#   title: "Robotics Engineer"
#   summary: "Design and commission robotic cells for industrial clients."
#   location: "Remote"
#   type: "Full-time"
#   department: "Engineering"
#   ---
#
#   # Robotics Engineer
#
#   Role description here.
#
# The page auto-switches from evergreen CTA to listing mode when files exist.
